{"tid":2444872,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"陶傑提醒各位小心出席clubhouse 個蕭旭談","createTime":"2021-03-13T07:15:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T15:23:58.000Z","uid":115540,"like":32,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"fd07dc0c6f99827ef7765be643214b19340917ab","tid":2444872,"uid":115540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T07:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.hkgolden.media/comment/vo2n01l5.cda1onpjyey.41irqb2pu1s.atj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.hkgolden.media%2Fcomment%2Fvo2n01l5.cda1onpjyey.41irqb2pu1s.atj.jpg&h=2335b7af&s={SIZE}\" />還在問邀請碼？語音聊天社群Clubhouse爆紅，背後技術疑跟中國「聲網」有關<br />\n<br />\n//《風傳媒》報導，隨著與聲網的關係遭到披露，Clubhouse的隱私安全性也引發質疑，因為中國有立法要求境內公司提供蒐集數據。<br />\n<br />\n中國2017年通過的《國家情報法》，該法規定中國全體須協助情報蒐集，第10條寫道：「國家情報工作機構根據工作需要，依法使用必要的方式、手段和渠道，在境內外開展情報工作。」第14條指出：「國家情報工作機構可以要求有關機關、組織和公民提供必要的支持、協助和配合。」<br />\n<br />\n而Clubhouse要求用戶在註冊時提供手機號碼，並授權軟體開發商能檢視該用戶通訊錄上聯絡人列表，這意味著用戶的所有聯繫人都被記錄並存儲在開發商服務器上。另外如果Clubhouse使用聲網的技術，用戶資料與使用期間的聲音是否會被「送中」？香港媒體「Winandmac Media」嘗試聯繫Clubhouse公關，但尚未得到回覆。//"},{"pid":"5dd5ae0b0f00d8c5001dee08b86161c233b95705","tid":2444872,"uid":115540,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T07:34:17.000Z","msg":"真心提大家唔好講太多..."},{"pid":"42544490db5577a41f132a264b407bebeec78b64","tid":2444872,"uid":155431,"like":7,"dislike":22,"score":-15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T07:37:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HORST8M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHORST8M.jpg&h=1b31f5f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1c6dff7cc91e85f9699e35e93039e8e54c81003","tid":2444872,"uid":115540,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"42544490db5577a41f132a264b407bebeec78b64","tid":2444872,"uid":155431,"like":7,"dislike":22,"score":-15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T07:37:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HORST8M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHORS